name: Purridge Plush
description:
Purridge is the white cat who always makes her friends smile. A girl drummer who likes to play music and sports. Always wears her favorite orange-brown striped scarf anytime, anywhere. Don't let her calm appearance fool you, this gal can rock the drums and kick butt with her martial art skills.

-Handmade by Cheri herself in Torrance, CA with all new materials such as fleece, felt and polyester fiberfill. 
-Measures approximately 12" x 12" 
-Very Soft & cuddly

*As they are handmade, each doll features slight variations enhancing the dolls' uniqueness.

name: Ringo Plush
description:
Ringo is Purridge's best bud and bandmate back in Kittyville. A smart go-getter feline who wants to try new things. A techy geek turning nothing into something. Ringo spends a lot of time playing with gadgets and gizmos and tends to rock out loud on his electric guitar.

-Handmade by Cheri herself in Torrance, CA with all new materials such as fleece, felt and polyester fiberfill. 
-Measures approximately 12" x 12" 
-Very Soft & cuddly

*As they are handmade, each doll features slight variations enhancing the dolls' uniqueness.

name: Chef Tako Plush
description:
hef Tako is a sushi chef from Osaka, Japan. The friendly octopus owns his own sushi cafe. He loves photography, especially taking his fisheye camera anywhere he goes, driving his mini car. He deals with a lot of rolls: sushi rolls and film rolls, that's just how he rolls!

Energetic, flexible and vegetarian Ribbit.  Thinks eating green plants would maintain his green complexion.  He repairs and fixes anything, the handyfrog of the town.  Loves doing Yoga in his spare time.
